<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xml:lang="cn"><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="4.3.3">Jekyll</generator><link href="https://quaner-dev.github.io/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml"/><link href="https://quaner-dev.github.io/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" hreflang="cn"/><updated>2024-03-09T15:12:42+00:00</updated><id>https://quaner-dev.github.io/feed.xml</id><title type="html">blank</title><subtitle>A technical blog about daily summaries. </subtitle><entry><title type="html">LVM简介</title><link href="https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2024/LVM/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="LVM简介"/><published>2024-03-09T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2024-03-09T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2024/LVM</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2024/LVM/"><![CDATA[<h1 id="lvm">LVM</h1> <h2 id="lvm概念">LVM概念</h2> <h3 id="pv">PV</h3> <p>PV（Physical Volume）：物理卷，即实际存在的硬盘，分区或者RAID</p> <h3 id="vg">VG</h3> <p>VG（Volume Group）：卷组，由多个物理卷组合成的整体卷组</p> <h3 id="lv">LV</h3> <p>LV（Logical Volume）：逻辑卷，从卷组中分割出来，可以挂载的逻辑存储卷</p> <h2 id="lvm命令">LVM命令</h2> <table> <thead> <tr> <th>功能</th> <th>物理卷管理</th> <th>卷组管理</th> <th>逻辑卷管理</th> </tr> </thead> <tbody> <tr> <td>扫描</td> <td>pvscan</td> <td>vgscan</td> <td>lvscan</td> </tr> <tr> <td>建立</td> <td>pvcreate</td> <td>vgcreate</td> <td>lvcreate</td> </tr> <tr> <td>显示</td> <td>pvdisplay</td> <td>vgdisplay</td> <td>lvdisplay</td> </tr> <tr> <td>删除</td> <td>pvremote</td> <td>vgremote</td> <td>lvremove</td> </tr> <tr> <td>扩展</td> <td>物理卷无法扩展</td> <td>vgextend</td> <td>lvextend</td> </tr> <tr> <td>缩小</td> <td>物理卷无法缩小</td> <td>vgreduce</td> <td>lvreduce</td> </tr> </tbody> </table> <h2 id="lvm实战">LVM实战</h2> <h3 id="pvcreate">pvcreate</h3> <p><img src="/assets/img/blog_preview/2024-03-09-LVM/pvcreate.png" alt="pvcreate"/></p> <h3 id="pvremove">pvremove</h3> <p><img src="/assets/img/blog_preview/2024-03-09-LVM/pvremove.png" alt="pvremove"/></p> <h3 id="vgcreate">vgcreate</h3> <p><img src="/assets/img/blog_preview/2024-03-09-LVM/vgcreate.png" alt="vgcreate"/></p> <h3 id="vgremove">vgremove</h3> <p><img src="/assets/img/blog_preview/2024-03-09-LVM/vgremove.png" alt="vgremove"/></p> <h3 id="lvcreate">lvcreate</h3> <p><img src="/assets/img/blog_preview/2024-03-09-LVM/lvcreate.png" alt="lvcreate"/></p> <h3 id="lvremove">lvremove</h3> <p><img src="/assets/img/blog_preview/2024-03-09-LVM/lvremove.png" alt="lvremove"/></p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="LVM"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[介绍LVM使用]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Displaying External Posts on Your al-folio Blog</title><link href="https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2022/displaying-external-posts-on-your-al-folio-blog/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Displaying External Posts on Your al-folio Blog"/><published>2022-04-23T23:20:09+00:00</published><updated>2022-04-23T23:20:09+00:00</updated><id>https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2022/displaying-external-posts-on-your-al-folio-blog</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2022/displaying-external-posts-on-your-al-folio-blog/"><![CDATA[]]></content><author><name></name></author></entry></feed>